                <h1>Do Background Checks Include Driving Records?</h1>
                <p>Yes, background checks often include driving records, especially when the job involves driving responsibilities. Employers may review your driving history to assess your reliability and safety as a driver. This can include looking at violations, accidents, and license status, which can influence their hiring decisions.</p>
